{"tid":188813,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實曱甴眼中嘅人類係咪同鬼差唔多？","createTime":"2017-04-06T03:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T05:00:30.000Z","uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f363a438cb02d6132cc94f677a84c13b295deff1","tid":188813,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:32:05.000Z","msg":"好地地係夜晚係啲暗角位就唔會遇到人，但係一去啲open area 或者日光日白出街就會撞人。<br />\n<br />\n撞到人嘅時候會發生一啲自己理解唔到嘅野，一時會有尖叫聲，一時會有啲野周圍郁亂咁飛，每次都唔同。無惡意嘅就嚇一嚇你跟住就會唔知去左邊，但唔好彩撞到惡嘅人就會攻擊自己。比人搞嘅同類死狀都好恐怖，粉身碎骨、浸死、甚至死無全屍。<br />\n<br />\n人類會set 一啲有詛咒嘅野係周圍，掂到、食到就會莫名其妙地死亡，有時仲會傳染到成家都賴嘢。有啲凶"},{"pid":"72b2ebbbf4467361f001ba23964fc1407f48c097","tid":188813,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:33:20.000Z","msg":"凶宅叫曱甴屋點都唔可以入，有曱甴係入面死過，入左去多數出唔番黎。"},{"pid":"fbc38dd2951395d4b5f911474b17c66df1d45db6","tid":188813,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:33:58.000Z","msg":"我地係鬼眼中會唔會只係曱甴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1d75250dcd9f3bd1178a0760d8a058e7c3ece8","tid":188813,"uid":88371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:39:11.000Z","msg":"正解"},{"pid":"a5054e19e1f7ff07b09d00fd3568712eb296d0bc","tid":188813,"uid":81498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:45:06.000Z","msg":"有趣想法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d114a13cbde58fd7712c2202e5be1ce389dc1355","tid":188813,"uid":2386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:00:30.000Z","msg":"如果康德冇講錯<br />\n曱甴係冇知性同理性<br />\n所以唔會有以上嘅諗法"}]}